  <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
      var stri = window.parent.location.href;
      var strii = stri.indexOf('?');
      if (strii != -1) {
          var indexe = stri.substring(stri.indexOf('=') + 1);
          var pagename = indexe.substring(indexe.indexOf('/') + 1);
          window.location.href = '../index.html#PageName=' + pagename;
      }
     
  </script>
<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Consent for Blood Transfusion Entry </h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the patient blood consent transfusion details.
<br />
<hr /><br />
<img src="images/BB_Con_Transfusion_E.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr /><br />
<img src="images/BB_Con_Transfusion_D.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>
<span class="title">Search (Button): </span><br />
    User can search the records based on the Service No,Rank,A&D No,First Name,Last Name,Hin.Click on the particuler record for which you want to do the entry.
<br />
<span class="title">GRID (Display): </span> <br />
   Based on search criteria data will display in the form of table. At a time only five (5) records will be displayed. To navigate or look for the next record pagination (the system of numbering pages) will be there. 
<br />
    <span class="title">OK Button and Text Box: </span> 
    <br />If user wants to switch directly to any particular page no, then he can simply enter the page no. in the given text box and click on OK Button.
<br />
<span class="title"> Service Personnel Details section: </span><br />
This section will show the details like- Service Type,Service No.,Service Status,Relation,Ser. Per. Name,Rank etc.
<br />
<span class="title">Patient Details section: </span> <br />
   This section will show the following detail of the patient like - HIN No.,Patient Name,Sex,Age,Marital Status,Religion,District etc. <br />
    <span class="title">  Blood Component Name drop down box: </span> 
    <br />User can select Blood Component Name from the drop down box, this is mendatory field.
<br />
     <span class="title">Witness Name Text Box:</span> 
    <br />User can write witness Name in this text box.
    <br />
    
    <span class="title">Add (Button): </span> 
    <br />By clicking on Add button user can Add the data.
<br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button): </span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data.
<br />
  
</p>

</div>
